1. Project Overview

This project is a web-based reward earning platform where users can create accounts, complete tasks, earn rewards, refer friends, and request withdrawals.

The platform includes both a user dashboard and an admin panel.

The goal of the project is to build a scalable low-cost earning platform capable of supporting thousands of users while keeping hosting and backend costs minimal.

2. Main Objectives
Allow users to register and log in securely
Allow users to complete earning tasks
Provide referral-based rewards
Allow users to request withdrawals
Allow admins to manage users and withdrawals
Create a modern responsive UI
Use free or low-cost cloud services initially
3. Technology Stack
Frontend
Next.js
HTML
CSS
JavaScript
Tailwind CSS
Backend
Supabase
Authentication
Supabase Authentication
Hosting
Vercel
Cloudflare Pages (optional frontend hosting)
4. User Features
4.1 User Registration

Users can:

Create a new account
Register using email and password
Log in securely
Log out
Reset password
4.2 User Dashboard

The dashboard should display:

User profile information
Wallet balance
Completed tasks
Referral earnings
Withdrawal history
Available tasks
4.3 Earning Tasks

Users can:

View available tasks
Complete tasks
Receive rewards after task completion
Track completed tasks

Task types may include:

Watching ads
Visiting websites
Clicking links
Completing offers
Referral tasks
4.4 Referral System

Users receive:

A unique referral link
Referral bonus after successful signup
Additional earnings for referral activity

Referral features:

Referral count
Referral earnings history
Referral statistics
4.5 Wallet System

The wallet should:

Display current balance
Display earnings history
Display withdrawal history
Update automatically after rewards
4.6 Withdrawals

Users can:

Request withdrawals
View withdrawal status
Cancel pending withdrawals (optional)

Withdrawal statuses:

Pending
Approved
Rejected
Paid

Minimum withdrawal amount:

₹100
5. Admin Panel Features
5.1 Admin Authentication

Admins must:

Log in securely
Access protected admin routes
5.2 Dashboard Overview

Admin dashboard should display:

Total users
Total earnings
Pending withdrawals
Completed withdrawals
Site statistics
5.3 User Management

Admins can:

View users
Ban users
Delete users
Edit user balances
View referral information
5.4 Withdrawal Management

Admins can:

Approve withdrawals
Reject withdrawals
Mark withdrawals as paid
View withdrawal requests
5.5 Task Management

Admins can:

Add tasks
Edit tasks
Delete tasks
Set task rewards
6. Database Structure

Main database tables:

users

Stores:

User profile
Email
Balance
Referral code
Account status
tasks

Stores:

Task information
Reward amount
Task status
completed_tasks

Stores:

Completed task history
User task records
withdrawals

Stores:

Withdrawal requests
Payment status
Withdrawal amount
referrals

Stores:

Referral relationships
Referral bonuses
7. Security Requirements

The application should:

Protect admin routes
Use authentication middleware
Prevent unauthorized access
Validate all form inputs
Secure API routes
Protect against spam and abuse
8. UI/UX Requirements

The platform should:

Be mobile responsive
Have a clean modern design
Load quickly
Support desktop and mobile devices
Use easy navigation
9. Performance Goals

The system should:

Support 2000–3000 users per day initially
Use free-tier infrastructure when possible
Scale later if traffic increases
10. Future Improvements

Possible future features:

Daily bonuses
Leaderboards
Push notifications
Multiple withdrawal methods
AI-based fraud detection
Multi-language support
Mobile application
11. Deployment Requirements

Deployment platforms:

Vercel
Cloudflare Pages

Environment variables should be configured securely.

12. Testing Requirements

The application should be tested for:

Authentication flow
Dashboard loading
Task completion
Referral tracking
Withdrawal system
Admin panel security
Database operations
Mobile responsiveness
13. Project Goal Summary

The goal is to create a scalable earning platform with:

Modern UI
Secure authentication
Reward-based earning system
Referral system
Admin management system
Low initial operational cost
Future scalability